title: Death Squad. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: January 23rd, 2015

Description:

Ryan Willburn is a rebel war agent forced to go against an oppressive government to expose their war crimes. To avoid capture, Willburn must face a vicious death squad of mercenaries who are prepared to sacrifice their lives rather than see him get out alive.

Director: Alessandro Capone

Writers: Tommaso Agnese, Luca D'Alisera

Actors: Danny Glover, Daryl Hannah, Michael Madsen, Stephen Baldwin, Rutger Hauer

Genre: Action and Adventure, Science Fiction

Run Time: 1 hour 30 minutes
